    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "COLFAX, July 26.-Prosecuting\nAttorney Kipp has sent word to\nthe various city marshals in Whit\nman county to arrest all Migrants\nand prosecute them. The towns\nare filled with men pretending to\nlook for work but who do not want\nto find it. Such men will be put\nto work on county concrete. Real\nlaborers and harvest hands are in\nvited to Whitman county."
    }
